00:00:06.880 --> 00:00:09.491
today we will make urad dal ladoo.

00:00:09.724 --> 00:00:12.962
urad dal ladoo are prepared with three ways.

00:00:13.291 --> 00:00:18.013
first by roasting urad dal or mogra and then make ladoo.

00:00:18.161 --> 00:00:22.939
second by soaking,grinding, roasting urad dal and then make ladoo.

00:00:23.135 --> 00:00:29.445
third by grinding dry urad dal,make flour from it and then make ladoos.

00:00:29.776 --> 00:00:35.379
today we will make ladoo by grinding urad dal and make flour from it,then make ladoos

00:00:35.752 --> 00:00:41.863
let's see what all ingredients are required for making urad dal laddo.

00:00:42.370 --> 00:00:44.354
uard dal - 1 cup

00:00:45.151 --> 00:00:47.722
boora or tagar - 1 cup

00:00:48.287 --> 00:00:49.795
ghee - 1/2 cup

00:00:50.355 --> 00:00:52.799
green cardamom - 4-5 (powdered)

00:00:53.112 --> 00:00:54.636
cashew nuts - 8-10

00:00:55.016 --> 00:00:56.024
almonds - 8-10

00:00:57.021 --> 00:00:59.505
cut cashew nuts and almonds thinly.

00:01:00.325 --> 00:01:05.349
for making ladoos roast the dal first.

00:01:18.533 --> 00:01:21.350
pan is heated add urad dal into it.

00:01:31.737 --> 00:01:37.150
stir constantly and roast the dal until ut turns little brown in color.

00:01:37.332 --> 00:01:42.895
you can also use whole urad lentils but they should be without skin.

00:01:52.378 --> 00:01:58.711
dal is roasted;turn off the gas.

00:01:58.940 --> 00:02:03.083
after dal gets little frigid ground to make flour.

00:02:04.747 --> 00:02:10.199
meanwhile cut cashew nuts and almonds.

00:02:13.924 --> 00:02:17.361
now ground the dal.

00:02:36.432 --> 00:02:42.385
flour it ready;keep it bit coarse and not like that of maida.

00:02:51.992 --> 00:02:53.611
melt ghee.

00:03:07.110 --> 00:03:10.117
add boora in flour.

00:03:10.639 --> 00:03:16.798
boora and tagar are best to be used for making ladoo. ladoo made with powdered sugar will not taste pleasing.

00:03:17.262 --> 00:03:23.821
boora and tagar are easily available in markets but if you don't find for

00:03:23.847 --> 00:03:29.962
yourself then logon to nishamadhulika.com for method of making tagar.

00:03:42.029 --> 00:03:45.196
add cardamom powder and mix all ingredients nicely.

00:03:51.802 --> 00:03:55.485
quantity of boora or tagar can be increased or decreased as per your choice.

00:04:01.137 --> 00:04:05.463
ghee is melted now add it in flour.

00:04:24.955 --> 00:04:32.293
now try making ladoo;if you are not able to bind ladoos then add some more amout of ghee in the mixture.

00:04:40.308 --> 00:04:47.017
if you are able to bind ladoos then there is no need to add more ghee.

00:04:50.328 --> 00:05:00.466
take little amount of mixture and make ladoos small or big ladoos as per your choice

00:05:15.451 --> 00:05:17.603
lentils are very nutritious.

00:05:19.996 --> 00:05:24.012
these ladoos are very healthy and are consumed during winters.

00:05:54.843 --> 00:05:56.645
ladoos are now ready.

00:05:59.903 --> 00:06:03.562
while making urad dal ladoo keep note of few things.

00:06:03.829 --> 00:06:10.443
when adding ghee in flour don't add it altogether else it will thin.

00:06:10.782 --> 00:06:16.210
so add little amount of ghee at a time and stop adding when you are avle to bind ladoos.

00:06:29.243 --> 00:06:34.918
store these ladoos in air tight container and enjoy eating for up to 2 months.

